Package: gxkb
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: X11 keyboard indicator and switcher
 It shows a flag of current keyboard in a systray 
 area and allows you to switch to another one. 
 It's written in C and uses the GTK library (no GNOME is needed)
